I was hoping that someone would be kind enough to explain the following registry related item.

If you cant register mpeg/mp3pro or ac3 over form (sony bug on some
machines), run keygen, generate your mpeg/mp3pro/ac3 serial, change into mpeg-mp3-ac3 registration over regfile folder and open the needed regfile with wordpad, delete the enter-your-serial-here text and insert your serial there, save the file and run it. thats all.
